Welcome Aboard!

Whether you’re headed to work, school, shopping or meeting friends, Monterey-Salinas Transit (MST) will take you there. MST provides bus service to the greater Monterey and Salinas areas as far south as Paso Robles and as far north as Watsonville and Gilroy. Our goal is to provide residents and visitors with high-quality transit service.

Our Brand Vision:

Connecting communities. Creating opportunity.

Being kind to our planet.
